    "longBusinessSummary": "Bank for Investment and Development of Vietnam Insurance Joint Stock Corporation engages in non-life insurance, reinsurance, financial investment, and other activities in Vietnam. The company offers health insurance, including combined personal, BIC care, worker's compensation, and 24/24 personal accident insurance products; travel and international travel insurance products; and car, motorcycle, home, and theft and burglary insurance products. It also provides corporate insurance, including ATM insurance, fire and special perils, compulsory fire and exploration, and property all risks insurance; constructors' all risk/erection all risk, contractors' plant and machinery, boiler and pressure vessel, and electronic equipment insurance; inland transit and import-export cargo insurance; marine hull, insurance for crew, and ship builder risk insurance; public and product liability insurance, and insurance for civil liabilities of shipowners; and money and surety bond insurance products. In addition, the company offers bancassurance, such as BIC Binh An and BIC home care insurance products. The company was founded in 2010 and is headquartered in Hanoi, Vietnam. Bank for Investment and Development of Vietnam Insurance Joint Stock Corporation is a subsidiary of Joint Stock Commercial Bank for Investment and Development of Vietnam.",
